      <div class="mainleft_title"> 
       <h1> 我有一个，关于你的梦 </h1> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_two"> 
       <div class="mainleft_from">
         作者：
        <a href="http://toutiao.weiyoubaba.com/m25055/">storybook</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; 发布时间：2016-09-15
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_three"> 
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; font-family: times; text-transform: uppercase; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; line-height: 25px; text-indent: 36px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></p>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.146875" data-w="640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMTzIDGSpN3Zl8Old43OEoubWoCJiawOooTnT6AZAyAspRAsX9dWnBackupWG7jNxEqNFKrL4NPg1DQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:微软雅黑"><span style="font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 21px;">不知道在哪里看过一个真实的故事，作者的父母结识在国共内战的时候，父亲是军人，母亲是普通人家的女儿。仅仅依靠几封信，他们就确定了婚姻关系。</span></span></p>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:微软雅黑"><span style="font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 21px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:微软雅黑"><span style="font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 21px;">而后，父亲请假回来几天完成结婚仪式，又回去他的军营。婚后的每年只见他的母亲一两次，每次也只有两三天。剩下的，是绵延不绝的书信。</span></span><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 21px;">直到作者已经成年，父母才结束异地团聚。而这么多年来光是父亲寄回来的信，已经有一座小山高。</span></p>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:微软雅黑"><span style="font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 21px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:微软雅黑"><span style="font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 21px;">在那个通讯不发达的年代，一封信的来回至少要半个月。但那时候的人们，似乎没有现在科技发展起来后的浮躁，能安安静静地守着心等一个不知道什么时候回家的人。对他们来说，认定的那个人是家，也是爱。就像木心说的：“从前的日色变得慢/ 车，马，邮件都慢/ 一生只够爱一个人”。 不管你是否也在谈着一段远距离恋爱，也许看看今晚的故事，你就会懂。</span></span></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px;"><br /></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">book君</span></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size:auto; letter-spacing: 3px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 5px; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: times; font-size:auto; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>
       <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(157, 157, 157); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; text-transform: uppercase; font-size:auto; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: times; font-size:auto; line-height: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br /></span></p>
       <p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; text-transform: uppercase; font-size:auto; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">远距离恋爱</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; font-family: times; text-transform: uppercase; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; line-height: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1313</span><strong style="padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; line-height: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">13</span><span style="margin-left: 2px; padding-right: 4px; padding-left: 4px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:auto; font-weight: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(208, 26, 25);">插画：许旺旺</span></strong></strong></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 25.6px;"><br /></span></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 25.6px;"><br /></span></p>
       <p style="line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 25.6px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5Jpv6Y4SWuG7aKtHicnbibmDQ1Ar8eq2Xtk5vRibDbol5NkZx5p0Sk7yO1Iw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">我还记得在电影《奔爱》里，年轻的冯裕健花费6年时间，只为能日本小樽的店里拥有制作寿司的资格。这样的梦很远，很虚无，也令我难以理解。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5JpQtvroqvY9ibrJn72q5yyABrlF6o8y6XVdSlBNfXncJYMf1TLrPNDrOQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">米饭和鱼生片难被完美结合，就这道手艺，他花费6年时间，才握出了一团合格的寿司米。当时并没有资格拿刀切片。冯裕健的梦是成为小樽师傅。而有一个女生的梦，是他。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5Jpyia5zzDYe6jVHbN0QYKLlecEaKEPhicQGggXge7Iw19Yicsw4F1icbhV7g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">而我也有一个梦。电影中的她，与我独自去找他的样子很像。我也曾暗自攒机票钱，拎着背包，悄悄出现在他的城市。这些，是我的特长。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5JpLzCEicicPibA8xk4vWOxlscz3sDRvVTVDmcbeUibYRJLzZiaJUQGXMAGNqA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">我经常和朋友吐槽，却在最后峰回路转地夸他不容易。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">“他说想我，我会立即跑去看机票，结果发现断食一个月也买不起。”<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">“但人就是不理智的，在被触动的瞬间会责怪自己的理智，然后又矛盾地筹钱，去见他。”<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">“不过他筹钱的速度总比我快。每次他突然出现在机场，都是在我们吵到</span></span><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px;">以为坚持不下去的那天。”</span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">“嗯，他也不容易啊。”<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5Jp25vh79aHMKGKYHkReBLGwjJmw6nW0mFZS0eHjSxl6HgVrGfazvznvg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">连结我们的，是微弱的电话讯号。有一晚我病了，恰好手机又没电。他连打了30几个电话呼叫失败，便丢失了以往的冷酷。在梦里的我都能梦见抓毛的他，正在连夜联络我所有的同城朋友。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">是啊，多爱都一样，我没有什么超能力能够立即知道他的状态。就需要靠微弱的电话讯号联系着。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5JpDI9oDgJ1TkKlbBPb1Hgt18PdArnpdhShdQ00wFKdD0PDC0A60jric5A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">到了他的城市，最难过的是别离时刻。他拿薯条蘸酱，递到我的嘴前。说，你不要不开心。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">我没有回答。他站起身，绕过桌子坐了过来。说，来，我们来拍照。不要伤心，我下次还回来找你。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">最后他还是先把我送到地铁，自己再回去搭车。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5JpLqibia1g0RAkibVz7nS93UXDOpk3C8QFnB3fNT3N4SfI9xKC4qSAZVScw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">临别之前，他总会递给我一个礼物。每次挥手之后，我躲在房里嗅着他留下的气味，拥抱有他体温存留的枕头。我翻开他留下的礼物，反复看着，好像爱就在身旁。<br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5M1AOOYqUMQYA4njbJfSSLgpxhicHq5JpbRC6rl75qWicqyFXGJZcOaPrmVbWJKtYZnG1KgJT6BfzsNhstXCLIVg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="900" /><br /><br /></span></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#595959;font-family:arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 32px;">我依旧会在风大又冷的冬天，伸出手来回复微信。嘴唇干裂，看到信息还是会咧嘴傻笑。尽管他没有在我身旁，但留下的东西，却重重包围了我。</span></span><span style="line-height: 25.6px;"><br /></span></p>
       <p style="padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 32px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: arial, sans-serif;"><br /></span></p>
